data.description: Beautiful brick home located in the Villages of Creek Colony. Home is Move-In Ready! Recent updates include a NEW Roof! Updated kitchen w/ NEW Granite Counters, NEW Tile Backsplash & NEW Stainless Steel. Fresh paint throughout the interior & ALL NEW Flooring throughout home. NEW Granite in all full baths. Many NEW Lighting Fixtures including NEW Ceiling Fans in all bedrooms. This spacious home offers a grand 2-story entry which opens to large family room w/ fireplace. Formal dining room off of foyer. Kitchen features an adjacent breakfast room. Primary suite downstairs. Ensuite features a tub, separate shower, double sinks, & walk in closet. A large 23x12 sunroom features two ceiling fans and over looks the backyard. Upstairs, a large game room shares the 2nd floor w/ 4 bedrooms & 2 full baths. All bedrooms have walk in closets. Seller willing to pay for a 2/1 Interest rate buy down with preferred lender!!
